gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 108, Nets 81
gameRecap.excerpt: Orlando defeats Brooklyn, 108-81. For Orlando, Franz Wagner led the way with 21 points, five rebounds, and five assists aided by Moritz Wagner (16 points, five rebounds) in the victory. Dennis Schroder led the way with 15 points and two assists with Trendon Watford adding 14 points and seven rebounds for Brooklyn in the losing effort. Orlando wins and improves to 33-26 on the season, while Brooklyn moves to 22-36 with the loss.
